                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="en" type="desc">Commentary on Hippocratic Aphorisms</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar">شرح فصول أبقراط</title>
                     <title xml:lang="en" type="alt">Sharḥ Fuṣūl Abuqrāṭ</title>
                     <note>Original manuscript in BNF.</note>
                     <note>This is a lemmatically arranged commentary. The introduction begins on<locus>f. 1b</locus>; the beginning of each Book is as follows: Bk1: 2b; Bk2: 22a; Bk3: 43a; Bk4: 57a; Bk5: 86b; Bk6: 111b; Bk7: 138b.</note>
